. The school has swimming lessons with clothes on. The council members visit a burger joint, and later do karaoke.  To practice saving energy, Aria has the council members camp at her family\u2019s private island. Uomi visits the Tsuda family during summer vacation. The judo club holds practice using Aria\u2019s love doll as a dummy partner. The council members make ice cream at the Tsuda house. Shino has Takatoshi clean the school bathrooms.\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 9\n | RelDate         = October 17, 2013<ref name=\"vol9rel\">{{cite web|url=https://kc.kodansha.co.jp/product?item=0000018134|script-title=ja:\u751f\u5f92\u4f1a\u5f79\u54e1\u5171\uff08\uff19\uff09|trans-title=Seitokai Yakuindomo (9)|publisher=[[Kodansha]]|language=Japanese|accessdate=March 20, 2020}}</ref>\n | ISBN            = 978-4-06-358443-1\n | ChapterList     =\n* Chapters 211\u2013241 from ''Weekly Sh\u014dnen Magazine''\n | Summary         =\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 10\n | RelDate         = May 16, 2014<ref name=\"vol10rel\">{{cite web|url=https://kc.kodansha.co.jp/product?item=0000019172|script-title=ja:\u751f\u5f92\u4f1a\u5f79\u54e1\u5171\uff08\uff11\uff10\uff09|trans-title=Seitokai Yakuindomo (10)|publisher=[[Kodansha]]|language=Japanese|accessdate=March 20, 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"vol10limrel\">{{cite web|url=https://kc.kodansha.co.jp/product?item=0000039891|script-title=ja:\uff24\uff36\uff24\u4ed8\u304d\u3000\u751f\u5f92\u4f1a\u5f79\u54e1\u5171\uff08\uff11\uff10\uff09\u9650\u5b9a\u7248|trans-title=Seitokai Yakuindomo (10) limited edition|publisher=[[Kodansha]]|language=Japanese|accessdate=March 20, 2020}}</ref>\n | ISBN            = 978-4-06-395093-9\n | ISBN_note       = <br/>{{ISBN|978-4-06-358483-7}} (limited edition)\n | ChapterList     =\n | Summary         =\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 11\n | RelDate         = February 17, 2015<ref name=\"vol11rel\">{{cite web|url=https://kc.kodansha.co.jp/product?item=0000019393|scrip